state department.

06:34.795 --> 06:37.095
Since there's a good chance
that things could become

06:37.097 --> 06:38.397
Tense over the next few days...

06:38.399 --> 06:39.798
I'm here to
keep these guys

06:39.800 --> 06:42.134
Away from each other's throats
and at the bargaining table.

06:42.136 --> 06:43.969
Great. Right now we need
to get these men in front

06:43.971 --> 06:46.004
Of the green screens and
make it look like they're back

06:46.006 --> 06:47.606
In their home countries
and not here.

06:47.608 --> 06:49.574
Anything gets lost
in translation,

06:49.576 --> 06:50.475
We'll reach out.

06:50.477 --> 06:51.843
Understood.

06:51.845 --> 06:54.780
Paige:
